column5: What a beautiful looking pup, I'm sure she will bring you a lot of joy (among other things).
Congratulations on your new best buddy.  Really sweet looking pup.
Enjoy your next 2 years of hell on earth!!
un conditional love. enjoy... labs live to please. after they teeth.lol

I almost didn't open this post....I was sure you were going tell us of having to put a dog down ( a horrible thing to experience). Instead, I nervously opened it to the sight of a goergous pup!  Great!!
Beautiful pup you have there . They sure are a handful for the first year but well worth it .
What a great looking pup, congrats !
Chocolate labs are smart. As Daisy grows up, she will test the limits a lot.
Congrats on your new fishing buddy

Labs are a wonderful dog.  I had 2 in my household when I was a youngster.  I also had a golden retriever, smartest dog I ever knew.  Smarter than me! - wouldn't take much??  Good luck with your new pup.
Nice pup. The puppy never leaves Chocolate Lab's
Cute pup! Dont let her boss you around! She will!! LOL  S.
